Class Contestant

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.Contestant

  • public class Contestant
extends java.lang.Object
    The contestant class will be used to create a person who will be competing in the actual game of survivor, and can be chosen by people from the User class.
    Author:
    Kevin Brightwell, Jonathon Demelo, Graem Littleton, Justin McDonald, Ramesh Raj
